  <ThingDef ParentName="LeatherBase">
    <defName>RT_BioSilk</defName>
    <label>biosilk</label>
    <description>Green, slightly transparent silk, made from refining the resinous substance that most metroids produce. It is provides exceptional heat insulation, but is more often used as a symbol of wealth than anything else. The refining process produces a faint hexagonal pattern, but isn't generally visible when weaved into objects.</description>
